# Nestjs Response Manipulation

1. Skip/hide/export properties on response that is sent out using class-transform serialization
2. Run validations on Response using class-validator async validate() function
3. Modify response direcctly using express Response Object. No need to return
4. Modify response using nestjs Interceptor post-processing primitive
5. Response validation using DTOs
